FBIS4-54549 "dreeu085_b_94001" FBIS-EEU-94-085 Daily Report 3 May 1994 BULGARIA Defense Minister Denies Intent To Resign Defense Minister Denies Intent To Resign AU0305103094 Sofia Khorizont Radio Network in Bulgarian 0900 GMT 3 May 94 AU0305103094 Sofia Khorizont Radio Network Bulgarian BFN [Text] Regarding a recent report, according to which Defense Minister Valentin Aleksandrov will resign, today Minister Aleksandrov personally stated in the Konkurenti [Competitors] program of Khorizont Radio that he does not intend to resign unless Prime Minister Lyuben Berov asks him to.
